#
# Evaluate these expressions: (no negative numbers are involved)
#
# a)    [`` [$a]+[$b]-[$c]=  ``]  [________]{$ans2} 
#
# b)    [`` [$a]-[$b]+[$c]=  ``]  [________]{$ans1} 
#
